  "invariants": [
    "Every tool in ReadOnlyTools() must have a matching case in resolveRoute (enforced by TestEveryRegisteredToolHasDispatchRoute)",
    "Tool responses and HTTP query responses share the same truth — dispatchTool calls through the same handler.ServeHTTP the HTTP API uses",
    "parseCanonicalEnvelope requires data, truth, and error keys to be present; partial envelopes fall back to plain JSON",
    "normalizeQualifiedIdentifier strips the 'workload:' prefix before building service path segments (dispatch.go:168)",
    "query.EnvelopeMIMEType is the MIME type of the embedded resource block in MCP tool results (server.go:389)",
    "stdio transport does not start an HTTP listener; SSE sessions and handleSSE are not reachable in stdio mode"
  ],
